{"tid":1553771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依張嘢搞到好多外傭以為真係唔可以響街放假","createTime":"2019-09-08T17:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T18:06:58.000Z","uid":59815,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5077266617906f7f3676d51edcf2eab3f87bfda","tid":1553771,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"有手足貼左依張野出街，好多張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPR4wUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPR4wUx.jpg&h=4c2318b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明手足或者想諷刺黑警，但係班姐姐見到，問埋人地中文點解，佢地真係會驚架。班姐姐一星期先得半日假，唔好咁嚇佢地啦。<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實外傭d工會都好撐香港人抗爭，會諗起菲律賓1980年代既抗爭。（東亞、東南亞在80年代的民主化同人民抗爭，菲律賓是最早的）<br />\n<br />\n希望手足諗諗。這不是分化割席，只係唔想搞到幫香港人做野既姐姐。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"43456861b6893b18518ebaa89508aa35ef5d63fb","tid":1553771,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"「緊急」十八區中學人鏈聽朝要人 入嚟睇下有冇你舊校<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553681\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d71766258089813765cf80facf83d78debd481e","tid":1553771,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:44:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94e97f3613a84993b90a3b504823729f5787af37","tid":1553771,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"推 2/20"},{"pid":"14532400b1c785f68d220e87cfc45138c928262a","tid":1553771,"uid":318397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外傭姐姐都係被壓迫既一群嚟架，更何況其實好多姐姐可能都唔知警方唔批不反對通知書呢件事，真係唔會知道係嘲諷"},{"pid":"e4d9f64d73b56a95247e0f1f0b3cb11fe0274976","tid":1553771,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"145324